Title: Rewa Nesting Table
Description: The Rewa Nesting Table is made from high-quality mango wood and rattan, giving it a unique and natural look. With its sturdy construction and stylish design, this table provides both functionality and aesthetic appeal to any space. Perfect for small homes or for entertaining guests.
Note: Please Note, Our handcrafted wooden products are designed to breathe with the seasons, so don't be surprised if you notice some delightful changes in their appearance due to natural shifts in humidity. It's all part of the wood's unique character.
Dimensions (Cms):
Large table: 70cm x 36cm x 70cm (WxHxD)
Small table: 50cm x 30cm x 50cm (WxHxD)
Table legs: 2cm x 2cm (WxD)
